flowchart LR
  U[User / AI Agent] --> FE[GoodChain Frontend
Stocks · Perps · Lend · Yield]
  FE --> API[GoodChain APIs]
  API --> GC[GoodChain L2 Contracts]

  ET[eToro API
Market Data + Account + Orders] --> PS[Price Service
REST/WS + fallback]
  PS --> N[Normalizer
canonical quote + priceE8]
  N --> QS[Oracle Signer Quorum
3-of-5 signatures]
  QS --> SO[StockOracleV2]
  SO --> GC

  GC --> GS[GoodStocks
synthetics + vault + AMM]
  GC --> GP[GoodPerps
stock perps]
  GC --> GL[GoodLend / GoodYield
stock collateral + yield]

  GS --> R[UnifiedRiskEngine]
  GP --> R
  GL --> R
  R --> CH[ClearingHouse
margin + liquidation]
  R --> HE[Off-chain Hedge Engine]
  HE --> ET
  ET --> RC[Reconciliation Worker]
  GC --> RC
  RC --> DASH[Risk Dashboard
alerts + kill switches]
  DASH --> GC

